  "title": "Chinese Language Teacher (Full-Time)",
  "description": "<p>Aiwen Culture is a premium Chinese learning centre located in Bukit Timah, offering 2–6 student small-group classes (P1–S4) and personalised Chinese learning programmes.</p><p>We focus on developing children’s language ability and cultural confidence, and through our unique 3-Dimensional ARTS Chinese Learning Method (Drawing · Calligraphy · Music), we help children fall in love with Chinese in a relaxed and enjoyable classroom environment.<br /><br />Responsibilities:</p><p>• Conduct small-group Chinese lessons for primary school students</p><p>• Prepare lesson materials and support students’ language development</p><p>• Communicate with parents on students’ learning progress</p><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>• Passion for teaching children</p><p>• Good command of spoken and written Chinese</p><p>• Prior teaching experience preferred</p>",
